-- ON THE MOVE-Citi Private Bank promotes Halé Behzadi 
-- 
-- Wed Oct 01, 2014 12:19PM EDT
-- None



Oct 1 (Reuters) - Citi Private Bank has promoted Halé Behzadi to global market manager of its North American unit's western region.

Behzadi will succeed Tracey Warson, who was promoted to head of Citi Private Bank, North America. Behzadi will report to Warson and be based in Los Angeles.